                  <span class="text-2xl text-[#4ECDC4]">üéÆ</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-[#F7F8F9]">Game Development</h3>
              <p class="text-[#D8DEE9]">
                2D and 3D games using open source game engines like Godot.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-[#D8DEE9] mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Engaging gameplay mechanics</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Focus on user experience</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Open source technology stack</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Art Development Card -->
          <div class="card bg-[#1E2432] shadow-lg">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-4 text-[#4ECDC4]">
                <div
                  class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#4ECDC4]/20 flex items-center justify-center"
                >
                  <span class="text-2xl text-[#4ECDC4]">üé®</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-[#F7F8F9]">Art Development</h3>
              <p class="text-[#D8DEE9]">
                2D/3D art, mockups, and visualizations for products and
                architecture.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-[#D8DEE9] mt-2 space-y-1">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Creative visual storytelling</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Technical precision</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Adaptable style approaches</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
