              <p class="text-[#D8DEE9]">
                We assess technical scope, feasibility, and create an estimated
                roadmap.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
              <span
                class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full -left-4 bg-[#4ECDC4] text-[#121620]"
