              <p class="text-[#D8DEE9]">
                Testing and quality control is integrated throughout our
                development process.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li class="mb-10 ml-6">
              <span
                class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 rounded-full -left-4 bg-[#4ECDC4] text-[#121620]"
                >6</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-[#F7F8F9]">Delivery</h3>
              <p class="text-[#D8DEE9]">
                We deploy the technology to web platforms or deliver to app
